OL,3,CWhat's behind the Budget tradition of
OL,4,Cthe chancellor's red box?
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, the Labour government
OL,7,Fwill unveil its first Budget in nearly
OL,8,F15 years, outlining the state of the
OL,9,Feconomy and explaining how it plans to
OL,10,Fspend and raise money across the
OL,11,Fcoming year.
OL,13,FChancellor Rachel Reeves will deliver
OL,14,Fthe annual Budget statement, a speech
OL,15,Fmade to MPs in the House of Commons
OL,16,Fwhich sets out the government's
OL,17,Fapproach to taxation and spending.
