OL,3,CWhat's behind the Budget tradition of
OL,4,Cthe chancellor's red box?
OL,6,FThe chancellor uses the distinctive
OL,7,Fred box to carry the Budget speech
OL,8,Ffrom their official residence in 11
OL,9,FDowning Street to the House of Commons.
OL,11,FEvery year, they pose on the steps of
OL,12,F11 Downing Street while photographs
OL,13,Fare taken of them holding the red box.
OL,15,FWhy does the Chancellor carry it?
