OL,3,CWhat's behind the Budget tradition of
OL,4,Cthe chancellor's red box?
OL,6,FThe word Budget originates from the
OL,7,Fold French word for little bag,
OL,8,F"bougette". The Budget statement has
OL,9,Fhistorically been brought to the
OL,10,FCommons in a leather bag, which has
OL,11,Fsince been replaced by the red box.
OL,13,FThe same wooden box, covered with
OL,14,Fscarlet leather and lined with black
OL,15,Fsatin, was hand-crafted in the 1860s
OL,16,Fand used for about 100 consecutive
OL,17,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
