OL,3,CWhat's behind the Budget tradition of
OL,4,Cthe chancellor's red box?
OL,6,FLord Callaghan broke with tradition in
OL,7,F1965 when he used a new box. Gordon
OL,8,FBrown later became the second
OL,9,Fchancellor to use a new box for the
OL,10,FBudget in 1997. A new red box was then
OL,11,Fused again by George Osbourne in 2011.
OL,13,FIs the red box only used for the
OL,14,FBudget?
OL,16,FRed boxes, also known as despatch
OL,17,Fboxes, are used on a daily basis by
OL,18,Fministers to transport official
OL,19,Fgovernment papers.
