OL,3,CWhat's behind the Budget tradition of
OL,4,Cthe chancellor's red box?
OL,6,FThey are lead lined to protect papers
OL,7,Finside - a feature designed in the
OL,8,Fpast to ensure the box sank if it fell
OL,9,Foverboard a ship which had been
OL,10,Fcaptured.
OL,12,FThe despatch boxes are also embossed
OL,13,Fwith the royal cypher of the reigning
OL,14,Fmonarch in gold.
